name: The lies you told
description:
I went to my friend's house. He is an owl.
After all the silence, he started talking and said with a laugh:
Telling the truth is not something that everyone believes in.
You are one of them.
I was confused and asked, "But I never lied to you!?"
He turned his head towards me and said:
That's right, but
Did you tell me the truth?
